# Agent conventions

- The opened workspace folder IS the project root — never create a wrapper subfolder for the whole app.
- Write files with `<file path="relative/path">` tags only. Complete file contents, not diffs.
- One shell command per `<run>` tag on Windows (no `&&` in PowerShell).
- Match existing project structure, naming, and stack.
- After creating files, prefer runnable entrypoints (`package.json`, `main.py`, `index.html`).
